---
// SectionInstalaciones.astro — Sección de instalaciones / "La Pared"
---

<section id="high" class="facilities-section">
  <div class="content-container facilities-grid">
    <div class="facilities-text">
      <h2 class="section-title">La Pared</h2>
      <p class="facilities-desc">
        Inspirada en la arista del Ama Dablam, nuestra arena vertical de
        construcción propia ofrece más de 20 vías de 5a a 8c+. No es solo un
        gimnasio; es un campo de entrenamiento técnico.
      </p>
      <ul class="features-list">
        <li>
          <span class="feature-line"></span><span>18 m de cara vertical</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="feature-line"></span><span>Desplomes negativos</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="feature-line"></span><span
            >Zonas de escalada en cabeza y autoaseguro</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="facilities-visual">
      <div class="visual-box">
        <div class="visual-overlay"></div>
        <div class="visual-content">
          <span class="visual-number">02</span>
          <p class="visual-quote">
            «La mejor instalación de entrenamiento indoor de la región.» —
            Alpine Mag
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  .facilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .facilities-grid {
      gap: 3rem;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .facilities-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .facilities-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #e5e7eb;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .features-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .features-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-line {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 4px;
    background-color: var(--clr-main);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .facilities-visual {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .facilities-visual {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  .visual-box {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    border: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .visual-box:hover .visual-overlay {
    background-color: transparent;
  }

  .visual-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-color: rgba(247, 127, 0, 0.1);
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
  }

  .visual-content {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    margin: 1rem;
    height: calc(100% - 2rem);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    position: relative;
  }

  .visual-number {
    font-size: 6rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    opacity: 0.1;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .visual-quote {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--clr-main);
  }
</style>
